::Shredder::

Shredder growls, seeing Quickstrike, Stingtra, and KitKat retreat 
back to base.He cosiders following them, but Megatron would certainly 
be displeased to see him. He turns around.

"See ya around," he says to Inferno and Jackle, flying off to base. 
He'd probably be recieved much better there, with Mante-. Shredder 
frowns. Why did she just pop into his mind? He shakes his head, 
continuing toward the destron base.
